                     <interp inst="t17881210-86-off380" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17881210-86-off380" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17881210-86-cd381" type="crimeDate">10th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17881210-86-off380 t17881210-86-cd381"></join> last, a gold watch, value 10 l. and two seals, value 6 d. and two ditto, value 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17881210-86-victim608" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Lightwood
                  <interp inst="t17881210-86-victim608" type="surname" value="Lightwood"></interp>
